text: Tigist Assefa Tessema (born December 3, 1996) is an Ethiopian middle-distance runner. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's 800 metres race; her time of 2:00.21 in the heats did not qualify her for the semifinals. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Ethiopian female middle-distance runners Category:Olympic athletes of Ethiopia Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics
